<div class="blog">
<div class="blogbody">

<p>Here is a tentative list of topics. Depending on how fast we go, the topics
may not appear exactly as planned. 
<ul>
  <li>week 1: Introduction; the Machine Learning Design Cycle 
  <li>week 2: Concept Learning; Decision Trees
  <li>week 3: Evaluation Methodology 
  <li>week 4: Linear Models: Regression
  <li>week 5: Linear Models: Classification
  <li>week 6: Neural Network 
  <li>week 7: Support Vector Machine 
  <li>week 8: Bayesian Learning
  <li>week 9: Midterm
  <li>week 10: Spring Break
  <li>week 11: Clustering 
  <li>week 12: Expectation Maximization
  <li>week 13: Dimensionality Reduction
  <li>week 14: Semi-Supervised Learning
  <li>week 15: Project Presentations
  <li>week 16: Final Exam Period
</ul>
